# Build artefacts (anywhere in the tree).
*.agdai
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.toc
*~

# Handoff notes / internal markdown are kept locally but not tracked.
# (The root README.md is exempted by the whitelist below.)
*.md

# Reference / generated PDFs are kept locally but not tracked.
*.pdf

# Whitelist policy: only the following files/dirs are tracked.
#   /BRA4/                   -- the active Agda codebase (.agda + .tex sources only)
#   /README.md               -- public project README
#   /goedelII-summary.pdf    -- built paper: Goedel II (linked from README)
#   /cgfun-cgfalse-note.pdf  -- built paper: Chaitin-Goedel I (linked from README)
#
# Everything else (including CLAUDE.md, bra-godelII.tex, BRA/ and BRA2/
# legacy editions, BRA4/*.md handoff notes, other *.pdf references, build
# artefacts, and /old/) is untracked.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/BRA4/
!/README.md
!/goedelII-summary.pdf
!/cgfun-cgfalse-note.pdf
